               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18101205-65-person679">
                  JARVIS 
                  STIRLING
               <interp inst="t18101205-65-person679" type="surname" value="STIRLING"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101205-65-person679" type="given" value="JARVIS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101205-65-person679" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at 88, Ratcliffe-highway.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you remember seeing the prisoner any time on the 1st of November - A. I saw him lurking about Mr. Francis's window; he put his fingers to the window and fetched out a piece of woollen cloth, I went and told Mr. Francis of it. I pursued the prisoner and overtook him in Ratcliffe-highway; I took him back to Mr. Francis's shop; I then sent for an officer, who took him in custody.</p>
               <p>
            
